{
  "texts": [
    "The questions are then entered into the ChatGPT interface, which begins the process of generating GPT answers.",
    "A prosthodontic specialist grades the responses obtained from ChatGPT based on their accuracy and relevance (47, 48).",
    "As a final step in the methodology, the graded answers are statistically analyzed to determine both the accuracy of the ChatGPT answer and the repeatability of the answers across multiple interactions.",
    "In the field of orthodontics, Subramanian et al.",
    "(49) demonstrate AI's potential to simplify cephalometric tracing for everyday clinical use and to conduct extensive data analysis for research."
  ]
}